;;
;; DESCRIPTION: Specifies all game-independent template TGI files.
;;
;; .LST FORMAT:
;; - each line is a filespec for TGI or LST files to load
;; - the wildcard character '*' can be used to load multiple files on one line
;; - they must be specified in the appropriate order, meaning templates first
;;
;; .LST LOADING PROCESS:
;; - the game automatically loads all "index*.lst" files in alphabetical order
;; - if you specify a LST file, it will be processed immediately at that
;;   point in the loading prior to the current LST file continuing.
;; 
;; USAGE:
;;  The engine loads in "index*.lst" so create one specific to your game
;;  and it should contain the following lines:
;; 
;;  Localization/*.tgi
;;  Game/resource_list.tgi	;; which defines [template ResourceList] required by these templates
;;	Templates.lst			;; this file
;;	All game-specific TGIs in the appropriate order
;;
;; REVISION HISTORY:
;; drp090402 – created
;; drp012903 - migrated to templates.lst from index_k2.lst
;;
